title: U.S. Cado Holdings, Inc. Recalls Imported Siluriformes Fish Products Distributed Without Meeting FSIS Requirements
summary: EDITORS NOTE: This release is being reissued to include specific identifying details on the products subject to the expansion of the recall on June 25, 2016. The first recall 052-2016 on June 20, 2016, recalled 25,760 pounds of frozen swai fillet products. The recall expansion...
